{"title":"可耻的旅行","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"可耻的旅行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鼠过街，人人喊打！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——民谚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贩卖战争的商人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"名字叫做艾奇逊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"离开美国到欧洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行可耻的阴谋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾奇逊到了巴黎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少都叹气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像是瘟疫来临"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像发现黑死病"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾奇逊做的买卖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是又下流又无耻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿人的性命当赌注"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从血海里捞取利润"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人讨厌艾奇逊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头巷尾贴着标语："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们不要看见你！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“战争贩子滚回去！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾奇逊到了伦敦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英国人民也不高兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的妇女抱着婴孩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到美国大使馆去送信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写了千千万万封信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信上表达一个意志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们要的是和平！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的妇女举着标语牌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的妇女拉开旗子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“禁止原子弹！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们的孩子不愿送死！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论在巴黎还是伦敦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艾奇逊都不敢出门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像毒蛇一样躲在洞里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也将像耗子一样溜走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不体面的访问！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可耻的旅行呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贩卖灾难的人人憎恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传战争的处处不欢迎。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}